This workflow is very easy to use.

----

You can control:
1. The prompt (choose the way to prompt in the Prompt selector)
2. Flux Guidance (3.5 is the standard)
3. LoRA's weights 
4. Sampler and Scheduler
5. Image size
6. Basic upscale (if not interested set it to 1.0)
7. Seed (fixed or random)
8. Face Detailer settings

Generated images will appear in the Preview Chooser node and in the large Image Compare node (both are saved).
If you want to use the Ultimate SD Upscaler you just need to click on the image you want to upascale and send (Progress selected image) it to the upscaler.
